# Regional data remapping

When API data has default + regional field pairs, **store raw API data** and rebuild UI text when language changes.

Field conventions (which field is Arabic vs English): see **`regional-language`** — reference data and request content differ.

---

## Required component pattern

1. **Store raw** — e.g. `rawDetails`, `rawCategories`, `statuses`, list rows unchanged.
2. **Build label maps** or map once — e.g. `buildStatusMaps()`, `buildCategoryMaps()`, `refreshDisplay()`.
3. **Subscribe** to `languageDirService.userLanguageCode$` → rebuild maps + refresh display.
4. **Do not** reload the API on language change unless the backend returned a single language only.

### Canonical list-style pattern

Reference: `facility-requests-list.component.ts`

```ts
// Language change
this.languageDirService.userLanguageCode$.subscribe(() => {
  this.buildStatusMaps();
  this.buildCategoryMaps();
  this.refreshDisplay(); // or rebuild row getters
});

// Maps use pickLocalizedField for reference data (convention 1)
this.statusLabelById[id] = this.localStorageService.pickLocalizedField(
  String(item.Name || ''),
  String(item.Name_Regional || ''),
);
```

Request **title** under a details header: read `Title` / `Title_Regional` from raw details with convention **2** (see `getRequestTitle()` in `facility-request-details.component.ts`).

---

## Avoid

- Mapping `name` / `title` / `description` once in `load()` and never updating on language change.
- Storing only the final displayed string when raw `*_Regional` fields exist.
- Multiple remap methods (`remapLocalizedContent`, `remapReferenceLabels`, …) — prefer **one** `refreshDisplay()` + small `build*Maps()` helpers.
- **Dual API parsing fallbacks** in components (`extractX` then `parseListFromResponse` then `Object.values`) — pick **one** approach in the **service** after confirming response shape.
- **Triple ID resolution fallbacks** — resolve from API/docs once; stamp missing parent IDs in the service when loading child lookups if needed.

---

## Forms

Do not remap active edit form controls on language change while the user may have unsaved edits.
